HOW TO BUILD portable_src
=================

System requirements
------------------

    - C compiler supporting the C99 standard
	
     mingw64, msys

     MinGW project on:
     http://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/

     msys project on
     https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/files/MSYS/

     Microsoft Visual Studio 2010.

 Build!
------------------
build x86:

make clean
/* Dynamic Linking of C Runtime Libraries with Vc11,If you are building the Firefox source code with Visual Studio 2012 */  
make CRT_LINK=1700 
/* else,Dynamic Linking of C Runtime Libraries with Vc10 */
make

build x64:

make clean
make BITS=64 CRT_LINK=1700
